{"product_id": "628800", "page": 1, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-12", "text": "Super Hydorah is a shining example of the retro kind of game you still want to play today. Graphics and sound are spot on to deliver the whole oldschool feel the game is going for. The game has an R-Type / Gradius kind of vibe to it, and also delivers on quantity and quality of content.\nThere are lots of different stages that all have a different theme to them. And that doesnt just mean different graphics, also different hazards and enemies. One time you have to navigate through an asteroid field, next time you take on a huge fleet of battleships, and then you fly through some plants that grow around you. So the game will give you a very diverse experience.\nEach time you beat a level, you also get a new primary-, secondary-, or bomb kind of weapon, and you can freely choose between those whenever you choose your next level. Yeah you can choose your next level too. There are different paths you can take to play through the game. Its not a very complex structure, but it is enough to give you some options to try out when you dont feel like you want to try a stage for the 5th time in a row. And until you became somewhat good at this game you will try and try again.\nIf oldschool shoot'em ups are your kind of thing, you need to play Super Hydorah. It is crafted with love and care.", "hours": 2.1, "compensation": "Product received for free", "user_id": "76561198003333568", "username": "karacho", "products": 628, "early_access": false}
