{"product_id": "734580", "page": 1, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-18", "text": "First impressions might put you off. Characters are cartoon-ish and a little crude. But persevere a little and discover a real cracker of a game. For the first hour or two, I felt totally bewildered, having little idea of what was going on and nearly rage quitted.  But the game has real depth and playability.\nStick with it. Search for the few guides available and it starts to make sense. It's an unusual blend of FPS and crafting and with some time and polishing I think this game could really be a winner. While it does need work, it's playable in it's present state and is better than many of the expensive totally crap, rip off games I've bought.\nRecommended.\n(Come on, it's even free FFS :>)", "hours": 5.6, "user_id": "76561197999411815", "username": "Growler", "products": 45, "early_access": true}
