{"page_order": 34, "recommended": true, "text": "Dear Community,\nthis autumn is full of great releases for Fernbus Coach Simulator, and I think we've proven that we're taking this long term project seriously with continuously making it better and adding new content. After releasing Fernbus Coach Simulator RELOADED\nand the free Usedom DLC\n, we're now ready for another blast: A brand new bus with the\n, the\n, as well as\nare all\n.\nLet's take a look:\n--\n(prices may vary depending on your region)\nIn this package, you will receive a fleet of\n. From compact to space-optimized, you will always find the right choice in this range of highdeckers, when driving your ambitious passengers on their travels through Europe. Thanks to the diversity of variants you will always find the right vehicle for the task at hand.\nThe cockpit is consistently designed for the comfort and well-being of the driver. Even at first glance, it exudes an exceptionally high quality. A modern instrumentation cluster, optimal visibility and operating logic come together with an above-average level of ergonomics.\nWe have refactored this trend-setting line of coaches with a lot of passion and love for attention to detail not just for its looks, but also with its distinct driving experience and soundscape with equal attention.\n:\n:\n:\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gXXTFHbEe3Y\nhttp://store.steampowered.com/app/724420/Fernbus_Simulator__Comfort_Class_HD/\n--\n(prices may vary depending on your region)\nFor everyone who is bored by the tedious noise along the highway, we've got something for your eardrums. The Fernbus Simulator Multimedia Package doesn't just contain\nbut, contains a\n,\nand\n!\nFlashBass FM is a fictional German-speaking radio station broadcasting all over Germany with a wide variety of mainstream music.\nhttp://store.steampowered.com/app/602730/Fernbus_Simulator__Multimedia_Package/\n--\nBest regards\nChris", "early_access": false}
