{"product_id": "427100", "page": 2, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "text": "Hey everyone,\nwe're very proud to announce that the Usedom DLC for Fernbus Coach Simulator is now available for all\nThe island of Usedom is the first free DLC for Fernbus Coach Simulator and contains two new destinations: The lido Ahlbeck and the city Usedom.\nUsedom lies on the Baltic See and is divided between Germany and Poland. Beside the two new destinations, the DLC also includes a new bus depot in the city of Wolgast including the Peene bridge.\nThe DLC is now available for all via Steam and should be added to the game automatically.\nWe hope you'll have a lot of fun! Please don't forget to leave your feedback: Usedom DLC - Feedback\nBest regards,\nChris\nhttp://store.steampowered.com/app/686280/Fernbus_Simulator__Usedom/", "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "427100", "page": 2, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "text": "This Hotfix solves some minor issues that came up after installing Update 1.15.\n:\nThis Hotfix is now available for all via Steam and is highly recommended.", "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "427100", "page": 2, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "text": "- The\nfor Fernbus Coach Simulator is now available!\nUpdate 1.15 updates Fernbus Simulator to Unreal Engine Version 4.16.3. This should especially bring optimized loading times. We have intensively worked on the performance of the game and improved it in many situations. Starting with loading times, over lighting and shadow rendering, to overall improvements in frame rates. The SkyDome and lighting systems have been improved with the help of your feedback. Thanks to all for the amazing help! Adding to that, many cities have been updated and partially expanded. The update also includes the brand new city of Stralsund. We've put a lot of effort in proving the AI traffic and adding new features to it. The physics and sound systems of all coaches have been improved as well for a more authentic and realistic experience.\nThere have been a lot of minor and major additional improvements and fixes, which you can read through in detail in the patch notes.\nWe hope you will enjoy this update and an overall improved Fernbus Coach Simulator Reloaded!\nYou can leave your feedback in our forum and add screenshots or videos: Update 1.15.15354 - Feedback & Bugs - Fernbus Simulator Reloaded\n--", "early_access": false}
