{"product_id": "597590", "page": 1, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-30", "text": "My Thoughts:\nAttack of the Bugs is a First Person wave based tower defense game and its actually really good. I was impressed with the different locations and variety in bugs. I certainly was not expecting the jump scares! One of the cool elements of this game is you can take childhood toys like the clockwork robots to use as defense, you also get to craft upgrades. The game starts simple enough but soon ramps up in challenges and  difficulty.\nVR Gameplay with commentary | Oculus + Touch | GTX 1060 (6GB)", "hours": 1.1, "compensation": "Product received for free", "username": "Paradise Decay", "products": 1761, "early_access": false}
