{"product_id": "718650", "page": 2, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-02", "text": "This is a strategy game/fantasy empire management sim similar to the old majesty series but highly updated and with many twists. If you enjoy those type of games you are in for a big big treat with this gem.  It plays well and I have not encountered any issues thus far.\nYou are a king or god type being who controls a single island, with your spells you can build bridges and pull other islands to you. Each island has a finite amount of resources and you can uncover more on each island.\nYou do not directly control your people but you can put flags that send your people to do things. There are many resources and all kinds of fun neat stuff. Even treasure to uncover!\nEach island is different and can even add things like monster nests to control, relics, and all kinds of things.\nTrust me just get it.", "hours": 5.2, "user_id": "76561197972461299", "username": "Mr.Prickly", "products": 255, "early_access": true}
