{"product_id": "628800", "page": 3, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-09-23", "text": "A love message to the 80's space shooter games. If you had the chance to enjoy some of the r-type, gradius, darius, thuderforce, etc. games, this is a mandatory buy. If not, this is a mandatory buy, as it compiles a lot of the best from those. Man, this is Hydorah even better and with 2 players!\nAlso we owe this to Locomalito. If you are intrested enough in the genere to be reading this, it's 100% sure you are going to have a ton of fun with this game.\nTotally recommended.", "hours": 8.9, "user_id": "76561198304792853", "username": "redcrowx", "products": 5, "early_access": false}
