{"product_id": "628800", "page": 3, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-09-22", "text": "You can tell that the people who made this game are really into Shoot'em up's.\nBoth Leveldesign and Sound Design are very well made. Especially the Music is outstanding.\nBut the best is the Gameplay! Controls are very responsive, they really put a lot of effort into this.\nIt's a challenging Game, but with a rewarding Gameplay. The more you play, the better you get and advance in further levels.\nPlus there's a nice 2 Player only Bonus Game included.\nRecommended to every shmup fan out there!", "hours": 4.9, "username": "Hiscorebob", "products": 465, "early_access": false}
