{"product_id": "718650", "page": 3, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-16", "text": "As of time of writing the game is in Early Access. And it already is a great little timekiller. I experienced no bugs, no issues, and finished a complete game. This is Early Access done right: You are part of the process of the game growing from a point where it already works well.\nSticking islands together is just a hell of a lot of fun. At its current stage the game is just a casual little adventure, yet it has a lot of potential to go a long way. Will watch this closely and am looking forward to updates & improvements!", "hours": 3.2, "user_id": "76561197968618383", "username": "Earl", "products": 111, "early_access": true}
{"product_id": "718650", "page": 3, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-16", "text": "I very rarely buy Early Access titles anymore after being badly burned in the past. Looking at you, DoubleFine Games! But then I saw this game and just could not resist picking it up. I'm really glad that I did because this is easily one of the best Early Access titles I've played.\nDriftland's graphics and mechanics are absolutely gorgeous. I just LOVE the ability to move islands around to build my empire. Everything is just so satisfying!\nThe game is also SO relaxing to play. I usually play on the slowest speed and just let things unfold, build my empire, and enjoy the music. Even though there is combat, it is not frenetic, so the game still feels peaceful overall.\nI'm looking forward to more content!", "hours": 25.8, "username": "sugarskull", "products": 414, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": true}
{"product_id": "427100", "page": 13, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "text": "To make the wait till Christmas Eve easier, we're launching a competition to win the Neoplan Skyliner for Fernbus Coach Simulator.\nWe're going to include three different christmas trucks in our upcoming update which should arrive pretty soon. Some of them are easy to find, some of them are not.\nWe uploaded a video with additional details about our giveaway, give it a shot!\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qd0V2U3H4KI\nGood luck, have fun!", "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "427100", "page": 13, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "text": "The latest patch contains tons of improvements and new content. From now on you'll have to share your lanes with AI coaches and semi-trailer trucks - these big trucks are an important part of our Christmas giveaway - Repaints are going to be accessible via Steam Workshop and tons of other stuff. Let's jump straight into the patch notes:\nWe'll provide guides for Steam Workshop pretty soon, stay tuned and discover our Workshop meanwhile!", "early_access": false}
