{"product_id": "512270", "page": 4, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-06", "text": "Usually I complain bitterly and refuse to even download any SHORT VR experiences... but I tried this one and was very impressed.  Yes it's very short but it's a very action packed immersive short experience and it makes an excellent showcase for VR.\nNice sound and visuals.  A very cinematic VR experience.  Excellent controls make you feel you're there grabbing on to things and pulling your body along in zero g.\nRecommended!", "hours": 0.2, "user_id": "76561197968559405", "username": "Pie Face Poo Face", "products": 255, "early_access": false}
