{"product_id": "706440", "page": 1, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-27", "text": "A correct game for its price, quickly here is why:\n- Good framerate.\n- I did not encounter any crash or bugs.\n- Unreal Engine 3.\n- Auto-shotgun with high accuracy, that's what I love in FPS.\n- Graphics are okay, cyborgs fight back.\n- Created by one dev.\nThe game is dark, it has a kind of sci-fi ambient with glowing effects here and here. There is no multiplayer but an arena mode to fight cyborgs for an unlimited time.\nStill, it will worth the price if you are looking for a little shooter.", "hours": 1.4, "username": "Kingohea", "products": 76, "early_access": false}
