{"product_id": "512270", "page": 6, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-30", "text": "Out of all the VR space games that I've played, this one seems to get the sense of scale of things just right, the ISS and Earth feel enormous and you definitely get an appreciation of just how small you are compared to these objects.", "hours": 0.8, "username": "Rykker", "products": 237, "early_access": false}
