{"product_id": "734580", "page": 7, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-02", "text": "1/10/2018\nAfter 35 hours, ive found this game great, Free2Play players can unlock almost everything it takes 30-40 hours to get 4-Star Rank, Iam currently 4 star now. which unlocks everything expect semi auto snipers, the stg and fg german spec-op guns (HOWEVER you can now craft a RADIO STATION and send up a signal flare with a pistol for the bomber to come drop you supplies WHICH can drop a crate filled with random equipment and SO YOU CAN UNLOCK ALL GUNS FREE-PLAY), a medium and heavy tank on each side..which when you make the rank you can build tanks anyways THREE 3 on each-side. I recommend BUYing the SPEC-OP dlcs or the german spec ops and the russian army dlc, as the classes come with 2 tnt, except one of the russian ones with the svt comes with 3 tnt which if you  get good tent spawns one person can wreck a Base with-in 20mins-2hours or more depends if the Enemy team is looking for you and defends/repairs the base. TNT is the best option for damaging bases..so far that i can tell, unless you have a heavy tank and a bunch of ammo.\nThere are some bugs, shooting is great unless you move then your just about not going to hit\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665.the closer they are the more of a lead you seem to need Some times my tent when placed to close to buildings spawns me in stuck to/ inside the building wall. takes time to craft tanks, its almost faster to loot from the houses, saves you alot of time but you still need to mining minerals.. the tanks arent to bad to craft its the extra fuel and ammo you need that cost alot.\nThe driving is funky, like some toy car that has no traction, friendlies with a biger tank can ram you and tip your tank or launch you into the air unrealisticly flinging you..no friendly fire\nYou can see teammates that are within mini map on your map, you also when aiming at them can see a small green outline on their bodies, which helps you know if its and enemy or teammate 300m away\nPretty Fun, It like rust and a heros and generals. theres loot and crafting. free game is great the pay just lets you unlock classes right away. Its quite fun i played 2 or so hours straight and still had fun.\nThis game is pretty fun and quick to download..you can mine wood and stone craft tents and walls and vechiles. matches can be 20mins to 4 hours. I didnt think a game like this would be so fun. At first its hard, i couldnt hit or see\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665.but it grows on you..once you get use to the gunplay. spawn in chop some wood and make a scavtent as a mobile spawn for you..build a few and you can click on the one you want active as a spawn. can see and have shoot someone from 395m. Like a RUST FOXHOLE BATTLEFIELD, Theres ways to use vechiles in factorys to mine material faster, i have yet to build a vechile. had almost all the gear for a 20mm and right when i put the loot into my tent a enemy 20mm drove thro and blow up my tent, lossing all the loot and 20-30mins of work..lol. I will keep playing this for sure.. I can only hope that the playerbase grows.\nThere are towers to capture called locator towers which show a big red ping circle where the enemy might be located. itll show them within 250-300m. All Weapons expext the semiauto snipers and the two german specops weaopons, and 1 medium tank on each team. You get to play as the germans or americans for free. LEVEL up, Rank and start to unlock new classes and vechiles. All weapons can be looted from buildings/bodies, and crates/which know can be called in by THE BOMBER(AI plane) that drops supply crates with radio sation and the flare pistol.", "hours": 45.2, "username": "DASman", "products": 144, "early_access": true}
