{"product_id": "724520", "page": 1, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-26", "text": "Edit: As of 12/11/17 I have been made aware of multiple severe bugs that can prevent you from progressing far into the game. Hopefully these will be fixed in a timely manner, so more people can enjoy a bug free experience.\n.\nMagilore, another free RPG I got a chance to try recently. I found it to be a decent free RPG, with a higher quality than what I would actually expect compared to a lot of the other free RPG games made in a similar style that I have tried lately. That being said I would still only recommend it if you are into free RPG maker style games.", "hours": 2.3, "compensation": "Product received for free", "username": "Kodyd194", "products": 181, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
