{"product_id": "734580", "page": 8, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-02", "text": "I've played a lot of freetoplay multiplayer games recently and I gotta say this one is my favorite.\nthe \"paytowin\" buisness model is kind of scummy, but not really that bad considering the \"dlc\" is only 1.99 and I haven't encountered any.  not sure if you can loot them inworld or from players so Idk.\nThe xp system is a double edged sword you feel like you're progressing..but then again you're like why can't I build this tank if I have all the materials, or if I can pick up the smg why don't I start with it?\nI mean it gives me a reason to keep playing and I KIIINda like it\nMy main gripe though is the first person hand models don't match anything it's like they changed styles midway.\nand also the characters are really brown (The germans wouldn't like that) so I feel like a buncha mexican wwII reinactors.", "hours": 6.2, "username": "Rudy", "products": 222, "early_access": true}
