{"product_id": "609150", "page": 4, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-20", "text": "I never write reviews, but i just have to for this game.\nMy god what a piece of uninspired garbage this dumpster fire of a game is.\nCharacters:\nI watch a lot of anime and play a lot of jrpgs so I've seen my share of clich\u00e9 and tropes, but by lord this game takes it to an annoying level. The characters all are so one dimensional and has no redeeming qualities, just straight up cardboard cutout. It's like the characters designer went into a DnD character randomizer and BAM we got our party. Honestly do the characters have any mind of their own besides being there to boost the ego of the main character Edge Maverick? (Yes that's really his name). Watching cut scenes all i can think to myself is \"don't choke sucking his\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665too hard now.\"\nMusic: Forgettable. It's not bad, but it's not good either.\nGameplay: So this is probably why you would want to buy this game, for the combat. But let me tell you even the combat in this game is \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ed. They introduce a system where you can time flank your enemy, but guess what? if they do an attack that's remotely close to you while you flank you still get spank. The biggest offender to me has to be the camera, like seriously how can you have action combat and can't even manually target who you want to hit? Playing melee in this game is garbage, one minute you're trying to attack an enemy that's literary right next to you, all of a sudden your character runs across the map trying to hit someone else, like WTF?\nPort:\nThis port is so freaking lazy, if you have your monitor at over 60hz refresh rate you have to change to 60hz every time you play this game or else you get micro stutters. God forbid you leave it at 120hz and the game runs at 2x speed LOL. Not to even mention the plethora of problems people are having in the community hub, this is 2017 don't call it a remastered if you can't even get the basics.\n\nFinal Thoughts:\nPlaying this game is like a test of patience, I can deal with so much before i get offended, and that's basically how i describe playing this game, it mocks your intelligence and offends you. This has got to be one of the worse games I've ever played, and I've played tons of games and jrpgs. Please don't support this garbage and spend your money on better games or better yet donate it to a charity of your choice, at least then you\u2019ll get more value out of your money.", "hours": 22.5, "user_id": "76561198015154057", "username": "Kurosama", "products": 15, "found_funny": 5, "early_access": false}
