{"product_id": "609150", "page": 5, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-16", "text": "For those having issues getting it running:\nFixes every issue thus far, adds Borderless Full Screen, Frame Rate x2 speeds, and adds DS4 Button Prompts (Steam sometimes doesn't recognize a DS4 controller by default) DS4 buttons are optional, if you dont need them then skip that step.\nFor crashes on startup: go to \"Control Panel\\Hardware and Sound > Sound\" select your default output device (speakers) find where you can select your audio output range and select 48,000hz (48khz) ((I personally have mine set to 24bit 48khz) and make sure to hit \"Apply\"\nMine crashed at startup due to the audio issue, when I got that taken care of I had the 2x speed with my 120hz monitor but the topic listed above fixed that for me. now it runs great at 4k + maxed settings! give it a try!\nI agree we shouldn't need to fix these issues ourselves, but I'd rather fix it myself and play, then get huffy and post a negative comment which solves nothing.", "hours": 49.5, "user_id": "76561198140039543", "username": "That Blind Person", "products": 67, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
