{"product_id": "734580", "page": 10, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-29", "text": "Oh Battlerush, you little game. So to start off, the possitives, The game is free so if you're thinking of getting it, get it and try it your self. The game is fun, feels a little like an old COD interms of the shooting style. you can build things, now mind your limited things like walls,bunkers, tents etc. ofcourse you have to go and get the resources your self but that is well balanced so it wont take you 4 days to build a bunker. Game at this point does not have much content but its still in alpha so dont expect much. The game has bugs quite a few but .ALPHA. so thats alright, how ever, if you want to have access to half of the contect then you'll have to play, but i think the prices are reasonable as the most expensive *DLC* its like 2\u00a3.\nOverall: The game is a decent time killer, you can have fun in it, but you need to learn what you have to do 1st, Its glitchy but the glitches sometimes make it fun, Its free SO, dont listen to reviews and go try it out your self.", "hours": 13.7, "user_id": "76561198172757703", "username": "Avamaste", "products": 103, "early_access": true}
