{"product_id": "734580", "page": 10, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-28", "text": "FROM MY INITIAL 6 HOURS OF PLAY I CAN SAY THIS IS A PRETTY ROUGH GAME BUT ITS FUN TO PLAY, THINK BF1942 MIXED WITH FORTNITE, AND A LITTLE DASH OF SQUAD IN IT..... PLAY THIS WITH SOME FRIENDS AND YOU WILL HAVE A GREAT TIME, PUT ALL YOUR RESOURCES TOGETHER, BUILD A BASE CAMP AND ATTACK THE ENEMY WITH TANKS AND JEEPS..... ALTHOUGH THERE IS A HUGE ADVANTAGE FOR LONG TIME PLAYERS AND ITS A BIT PAY2WIN (SNIPERS EVERYWHERE LOLZ) IT DOESNT HARM THE FUN AND THIS GAME SHOWS ALOT OF POTENTIAL... I COULD SEE THIS GAME BEEING ONE OF THE BREAKOUT INDIE GAMES OF 2018..... NUFF SAID", "hours": 9.2, "user_id": "76561198289313029", "username": "Fsociety.svenkaboy.exe", "products": 33, "early_access": true}
