{"product_id": "734580", "page": 12, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-23", "text": "Honestly, Why isn't this game on the charts. This game is still in its Alpha infancy, and its concepts and ideas already impose a promising future. Eventhough the servers are little and population is little to none, its a blast to play. Destructable environments, vehicles, and a buliding system create a immersive gameplay!\nHackers are not a impactful issue! I have not encountered a hacker yet.\nGun play isn't like COD, don't expect this game to aim like CS:GO.\nCoordinating attacks and advancing as a mini-army is satisfying.\nHonestly not a stomp P2W, DLCs give a slight advantage, but every player has a chance to be the star.\nI've got a decent amount of hours comparably to most negative reviews, you can support the developers by  buying the DLCs. The DLCS are not a money grab for the devs! They put the player first before anything, proof is the constant freqeuent updates and fixes they release.\nIf you're looking for a refined (bug-less, smoother GFX, populated) gaming expierience, come back in a couple of months, it's a game still in ALPHA!", "hours": 39.1, "username": "Bae N.", "products": 27, "early_access": true}
