{"product_id": "710520", "page": 1, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-25", "text": "At first glance this is an ordinary top-down shooter. But in fact it is something more.\nI want to start with humor, of course. He is here and always on business. As a bear who shoots balalaikas, a roar can stop enemies, and when his health decreases - he becomes stronger. There are a lot of game characters here. Each with its own characteristics. Not only do they differ in their characteristics, so they still have roles. For example, some characters rely on the main weapon, while others rely on the ability to damage or summon creatures. In total, I counted about 18 characters with unique abilities in the game. Many of them are parodies of different people. For example, there is a character who speaks broken Russian and is dressed in the uniform of the Russian police. Does not it remind anyone?\nAlso in the game quite a lot of different weapons. From the trivial automaton and the shotgun, to the \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing watermelon! Yes, there you can shoot anything. Scissors? Yes please! Maybe a fish? For all time of game to me constantly came across different weapon.\nI also can not pass by the conquest. Here in general you can arrange epic battles. Here you can hire allies, buy improvements and eventually meet with epic bosses. In general, the game has a lot of interesting things and I highly recommend this game.", "hours": 0.1, "user_id": "76561198037740410", "username": "gabella", "products": 47, "early_access": false}
