{"product_id": "734580", "page": 13, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-21", "text": "The game is obviously still in its early stages but with a few (maybe more than just a few..) bug fixes and updates this could become a great game. In it's current state it's already really fun and kept me playing for hours. It takes a while to level up which kinda sucks but the game is still very enjoyable even at level one. The dlc is also very cheap (compared to other games) however you have to buy the same thing for each of the teams if you dont plan on sticking to only one side. You can always just buy all the dlc together for a price that still isn't that bad. Even with the bugs, slow leveling, and somewhat annoying way they split up the dlc, I still really like this game and recommend it. I hope it only gets better!", "hours": 12.1, "username": "HornySpaceGecko", "products": 82, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": true}
