{"product_id": "734580", "page": 13, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-20", "text": "Really fun game, I absolutely love the survival aspect of it. Either fight for your country in the constant war going on, or go off on the sidelines to farm and build a base to defend. In this game, it is all up to you. Loot buildings and fallen enemies for gear, or farm and gather the natural resources on the map. Build weapons and gear or a base using the game's crafting system. No matter what, if you like WWII, survival games, or both, this game has something for you to enjoy!", "hours": 4.9, "user_id": "76561198055519132", "username": "|29th|Pte.Lightsaber33[G]", "products": 29, "early_access": true}
