{"product_id": "708340", "page": 1, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-24", "text": "I will definitely be checking in on this game with every patch. With all the silliness and weird clipping through walls, I couldnt stop laughing.\nThe highlight of my playing this game was the session where I clipped through the floor, way out of the map, made may way back by swimming through the nether, just to flop around the floor trying to angle a undermounted grenade launcher at the police while wearing my top hat, monocle and handle bar mustache. And I cant forget trying to use a grappling hook, which made me feel a lot like Spider-Shark.", "hours": 2.8, "username": "BushidoXWolf", "products": 274, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
