{"product_id": "378860", "page": 1, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-18", "text": "So far i really like this game its a big improvement over the first, the AI is still wack and the track limits are so all over the place it can be quite frustrating however this does have a majority of my fav cars and tracks so im happy. I love that we get Indy Cars! The Acura NSX! Civic Type R! Porsche 911 and 918, most GT3 cars.\nCars i would love to see in this game:\nFirst gen NSX\nPorsche 917k\nAcura TLX-GT\nMore Honda's\nDodge Viper\nMore Rallycross\nMore Trucks\nTracks i would love to see in this game:\nMid-Ohio Sport Track\nA drag strip for \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 and giggles\nPikes Peak\nMore Rally and dirt tracks\nOverall i give this game a 7/10\nIts a nice blend between arcade and simulator, once you get a feel for controls every car feels nice to drive, the tuning setup is a big improvement, i enjoy the track selection and cars, but its not my favourite racing game. If the AI and track limits get improved i'd give this game a solid 8 maybe 8.5", "hours": 10.3, "username": "DreadlordKai", "products": 816, "early_access": false}
