{"product_id": "378860", "page": 2, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-14", "text": "Im going to give PC2 a positive review BUT only if bought on-sale.  In its current state, it is not worth \u00a360ish.  There are still quite a few bugs although mainly only when playing online and the Licence system is terrible.  Having said that, the Single player Career is good and the variety of adjustable settings is great.  The tracks are good, the graphics are good and there are a decent amount of cars and race classes to choose from, even Rally X which is a nice touch.  I would reccommend buying a wheel and pedals though if you don't have them already.  I bought my wheel for this game and it made a huge difference to the gameplay.  In Summary; Good single player, Bad licence system and poor online play partly down to the Licence system.  If you buy this full price and add a reasonable wheel setup you'll be looking at around \u00a3250.", "hours": 244.9, "user_id": "76561198007258997", "username": "SpecialistZer0", "products": 56, "early_access": false}
