{"page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "text": "-Fixed a crash involving pet DB if not connected to the net.\n-Rip and pet restore are now fully automated\n-Cleaned up the serverlist class update code to prevent servers from displaying incorrect class information\n-Can now Left click hold on most mults to level them quickly\n-Enchanter Gear buff removed from Boots\n-Removed Token Mult from Tokens\n-Chest and Helm Re-scaled\n-Exotic will drop when killing a wallboss equal to your current max stage and the level will be +1000 over your current level. Basically a really nice rewarding upgrade for pushing.\n-Scaled down war stage skip\n-Re-scaled Class level system\n-Added Class Evolutions every 1000 class levels you will get a quest. Once quest is complete you can keep leveling and you will recieve 1 evolution gem to use to evolve heroes\n-Added Hero Evolutions Heroes now have 7 Rarity levels that can be leveled with Evolution gems each level gives them 1000x Base Damage. Heros will have different costs.\n-Added guild Tag to class boards. Blank names will appear til everyone is on current build.\n-Buffed Neck Gear by 100%\n-Ending Season those below 30k Max stage get x2 Returns those over get mixed returns.\n-Class levels and class XP reset, Token mult set to 3000 for everyone(buff to everyone except a few).\n-Gear Reset has been reset as well happy farming!\n-Enchanter now buffs helm and chest.", "early_access": false}
{"page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "text": "Game Version: ClickRaid518.9\n*Patch in progress*\n-Tweaked some serverlist update code\n-Added Pet backup to DB for new RiP ppl\n-Talent mults display on there respective present locations\n-Pet Talents now save on preset buttons\n-Quests in auto quest mode now show up differently so you don't confuse them\n-Auto Quest is getting an upgrade\n-Pet Talent Mult Increases by 1 at Pet Level 7, 30, 90, 365\n-Fixed a crash when trying to connect to a server that you arent able to connect to.\n-Slots with upgrades now show up with a Red Asterick\n-When displaying class rank it now displays the actual class...\n-Left and right arrow keys will now change talent presets.\n-Game no longer defaults to heroes menu on prestige.\n-Changed Order of classes in class scoreboard\n-You may now /invite someone whos in the Lobby to your game.\n-Can now leftclick inventory items in inventory to select them -thx PhatBoy", "early_access": false}
