{"product_id": "609150", "page": 11, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-06", "text": "Least favorite in the series and let me tell you i still \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing love this game. That says a lot that this is my least favorite of the entire series and i still love the game. Best had to be Till the end of time hands down not arguing with nobody on that. Id buy the entire collection if they put it on steam. Heck id play the Japanese Anamnesis if they put it on even though its mobile. Would love if they did what they did for Mobuis Final Fantasy for Star Ocean Anamnesis.", "hours": 22.8, "username": "Jarazz", "products": 474, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "609150", "page": 11, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-06", "text": "This game I wanted to like it, but in the end I did not.\nThe premise is intresting, but the main character is sooo boring,\nI hate him so much and you cant even change the field character who you will be\nstaring at for most of the game,\nYou can change leader, and choose who you wish to controle when batteling,\nBut you won't use that feature as the main character is the strongest party member,\nin your team compared to your female compenion,\nYou will get other party membmer later down the line, but still.\non another note, this game lacks dicection, you are tasked with an objective but no real guidence\nto where you have to go, does not matter if the path is liniar, but if you have multible path on a big map to take\nit's fustrating, that brings me to the map, you can enlarge it but you cant move it around to see\nwhat the map layout is like,\nWell that is all the ranting from me.\nthere are some positives the game has nice visuals and some\nnice music tracks. it also has decent voice acting.\nThere are side quetss you can take, but so far they are hard to find,\nWell these are all my toughts on this game so far.", "hours": 3.6, "user_id": "76561198007330588", "username": "Crisis", "products": 229, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
