{"product_id": "609150", "page": 11, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-05", "text": "Overall I am getting into this. I only have a few hours in so far of gameplay as most of it is just a movie, but I think I will like it as I go. I am only hesitant if a boss is way to hard as the combat I do not understand. I like the art, I like the JRPG aspect, and I like space so, so far I am into it and enjoying it. *Will update*\nSome small con's: Some of the art is odd as in massive tree thick necks and heads that are too big. Odd things like a girl with a man's voice at the beginning, odd controls for keyboard with no mouse use, many people saying there is no way to exit the game you have to crash out (fixed?) and a pretty odd combat system.\nStill a good game and I am hoping I will fall in love with it. Also I am doing a YouTube let's play on it as I go which I can link to in the future.", "hours": 1.2, "username": "Stormydove", "products": 233, "early_access": false}
