{"product_id": "378860", "page": 3, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-12", "text": "After playing Pcars in the rift I had to get Pcars 2 in the hope they would have fixed the issues i suffered in the first game.\nIssues:\n1.) Had to recalibrate my Driving Force GT sterring wheel each time I loaded the game - FIXED\n2.) A.I drivers crahed on first corner pretty much every race - FIXED\nImprovements:\n1.) Menus and U.I much improved\n2.) Car engine noise is now fantastic\n3.) Hosted 10 players of green to yellow strength connections plus 8 A.I on a 100Mbit/20Mbit and feedback from drivers was super psoititive and no lag issues.\n4.) VR awesome\nIssues:\n1.) Just a simple one, let the game remember the server name and password when rehosting as entering the names while wearing a headset is a pain.\nSo not much to complain about but heaps to like. I totally recommend this game to anyone using VR or who enjoys racing with friends.\nWell Done Slightly Mad Studios.", "hours": 33.7, "user_id": "76561197970626578", "username": "[SCu]Mattly", "products": 206, "early_access": false}
