{"product_id": "378860", "page": 4, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-08", "text": "Easily my favourite racing game,\nGraphics are sensational, the game really shines with the different weather conditions and times of day for racing\nEverything is customisable.\nThe race engineer feature taught me so much about tuning my car and getting so much more performance out of the vehicle.\nA large selection of tracks, with different variations for many of them.\nA good selection of vehicles that all handle very differently\nWeather conditions that effect the handling.\nSince playing Project CARS 2 I upgraded my racing wheel from an old DFGT to a g920\nBought new springs for the brakes and accelerator and bought a wheel stand, rather than using my desk.\nThis game has scratched the itch which Forza 7 failed to.\nI've become obsessed with sim racing like never before. and it's all because of this game.\nDo recommend.", "hours": 45.9, "username": "J i m p a c t e d", "products": 458, "early_access": false}
