{"product_id": "410380", "page": 5, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "text": "Welcome to a round up of the week! We have community tool birthdays, a slotted surprise, and more:\nHEX PvP Tools\nturned 1 year old last Tuesday. As a retrospective, Fred went over some truly impressive numbers in his forum birthday thread\n. The site is amazing, and if you haven't checked it out yet, you totally should. It is a wonderful place to learn more about the ever evolving HEX meta. Happy Birthday, HEX PvP Tools, and keep up the amazing work, Fred!\nWhile we are celebrating Fred's labor of love, we also wanted to take a moment and thank everyone for the amazing resources you have created over the years. Whether you've put together a collection manager\nor a wiki\n, a fansite\nor a shop\n, you bring our community together and make it easier to dive right into our game. To everyone who has worked on a community resource, be it an Auction\nHouse\ntracker or a content hub\n, thank you! You make HEX a great place to be.\nSpeaking of those who go above and beyond, InfamousNeo and our stream team are rallying once again for our annual Charity Stream! Over the past several years, they have raised over\nfor sick children. With your help, they hope to make that number grow. This year, the Charity Stream will run from the 26th to the 29th of October (full details here\n). There will be games, prizes, and giveaways, so mark your calendars! You won't want to miss it.\nIn honor of the charity stream, we will be granting everyone with an account by October 29th the 2017 Charity Sleeve! We will also be granting the stylish Diamond's Favor AA as well. This event has continually showcased the best side of our community. Let's show them what we're made of once again!\nWe are pleased to announce that with our next live update, we will be bringing everyone's character slots to 20! This is something our hardcore PvE players have been wanting for quite some time, and so we are going to double down and make it happen. With twice your character slots, we hope you will enjoy trying out more of our exciting race/class combinations as you work your way through the campaign. Enjoy!\nThis weekend is your\nto nab our Orchi-Notion and Massacre AAs. The format this month is\n. Tournament times are as follows:\nThe HEX Bash\nand HEX Clash\nare back once more! Saturday and Sunday, starting at 8am PT (Timezone Conversion\n), you have another chance to prove your mettle and walk away with cash and exclusive prizes! Will you end up a proud owner of fine cosmetics like last week's Bash\nor Clash\nwinners?\n\u00a0\nJoin us this weekend and find out!\nFor full details on prizing, please check out our tournament pages here\nand here\n.\nPlease note: if you happen to have technical issues with the Clash or Bash events, our support team requests that you submit an output log from that same day along with your ticket. This is essential, not only to ensure your ticket gets resolved in a timely fashion, but also to help us prevent similar problems from occurring in the future. Output, error, and crash logs can be found in the HEX: Shards of Fate program install folder on your machine.\nOur friends at IDW Publishing have launched an amazing Kickstarter \u2014 a print-only, 200 page, hardcover, quarterly comics & culture magazine called FULL BLEED. Everyone here at the office is signing up, so we wanted to let you know about it too! The first volume has an exclusive Stephen King interview in it, and this thing is ONLY on Kickstarter. Check it out!\nSee you in the battlegrounds~\nGot any questions? Want to chat with other players? Then discuss this article in our Forums\n! You can also follow us on Twitter, Facebook, our YouTube channel, or enjoy regular streams on our official Twitch channel\n.", "early_access": false}
