{"product_id": "410380", "page": 6, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "text": "Welcome to a round up of the week! We have our first Exalted player of the year, a brand new ladder season, and more:\nNo, not that kind\u2014it's the start of a brand new HEX ladder season! Here are a few of the fantastic prizes which you can win on your climb to Cosmic:\n\u00a0\nUp for grabs we have the animated sleeve you voted in as well as two delightfully new alternate arts. Start climbing now and nab them all.\nSee you on the ladder~\nWe are incredibly excited to be working with Sony to bring HEX to console and the game we all know and love to more players. That means more people to trade with, more people to play with, and more friends to be made! You can read the official announcement here\nalongside our CTO's response\n. Cory Jones will also be answering some of the questions you guys have about the PS4 client in the forums later this afternoon in his \"Friday Update Update.\"\nThe Highlands Battleboard will be rotating out of the Chark Mart next Friday, September 8th @ 10:00am PT. If you want to rock out in the rockies, make sure to grab it before it's gone. The Highlands Battleboard will be replaced soon with the cozy Coastline Battleboard:\nWash away your opponents by showing them you know how to have some real fun in the sun. A new board's on its way!\nThe HEX Bash\nand HEX Clash\nare back once more! Saturday and Sunday, starting at 8am PT (Timezone Conversion\n), you have another chance to prove your mettle and walk away with cash and exclusive prizes! Will you end up a proud owner of fine cosmetics like last week's Bash\nor Clash\nwinners?\n\u00a0\nJoin us this weekend and find out!\nFor full details on prizing, please check out our tournament pages here\nand here\n.\nOur first Exalted player this year is someone who has been around for quite some time. This person has been instrumental in putting together a tool that you probably use every day. Whether it's managing your collection, sharing decklists, or looking up cards, hex.tcgbrowser\nhas become such a large part of what it means to play HEX, it's hard to imagine what life would be like without it. For tireless efforts to bring us this amazing tool, we are pleased to announce that the category of Technical Exalted goes to Bogycoins (IGN: Romichete)!\nYou enrich everyone's playing experience. You've left your mark on the game and the community (quite literally!), which is why we are pleased to grant a vanity card in your honor. Thank you so much for everything you have done for HEX.\nSee you in the battlegrounds~\nGot any questions? Want to chat with other players? Then discuss this article in our Forums\n! You can also follow us on Twitter, Facebook, our YouTube channel, or enjoy regular streams on our official Twitch channel\n.", "early_access": false}
