{"product_id": "410380", "page": 8, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "text": "Welcome to a round up of the week!\nis out!!! Plus, we have VIP Sleeve Rotation, some news about our patch, and more!\nThat's right, over 300 new cards, 20 new champions, 10 new gems, and a revamped Frost Ring Arena are available now\n! What are you waiting for, join the fray! You can also check out our patch notes, here\n, if you want to dive into the nitty-gritty. Finally, don't forget that our Frostheart Release Celebration\nstarts today!\u00a0\nThe party will run until the 5th, and playing/winning tournaments during this time will award exclusive alternate arts. Jump right in!\nFor all you VIP subscribers out there, we have some news. The special sleeve granted to those signed up for a full year of VIP will be changing soon.\nYou have until July 22nd to get the Quash Ridge Tusker sleeve. After that date, the Tusker sleeve will be replaced with the terrible and magnificent Uruunaz. Note, if you get a year of VIP right now, you will get both sleeves!\nYou can learn more about our VIP program here\nor by visiting our VIP FAQ\n.\nSpeaking of sleeves, the poll for our 2017 Season 6 Sleeve Poll is now open! Vote for your favorite Alternate Art to become an animated sleeve reward for an upcoming ladder season.\nYour two beautiful choices this time around are Verdict of the Ancient Kings AA and Orchi-Naya AA. Don't delay, vote today\n!\nIf you want to reach for the stars, today is your last day! On June 30th, 11:59 PM Pacific, our 2017 ladder season #3 will roll over. This means that if you are aiming for a spot in our upcoming Cosmic Crown Showdown\n, or if you haven't finished grabbing your ladder rewards, it's climb time!\nRemember, players who reach Cosmic will get these exclusive AAA sleeves to honor their achievement. Grab yours before it's too late. Our next sleeve will be the Gallant Spearcliff you all voted for.\nNote that our upcoming ladder rewards will be\u00a0Gallant Spearcliff AA and Webborn Apostate AA:\nAnd as always, there are\u00a0packs, gold, and glory to earn as you climb in rank. Enjoy!\nThe HEX Clash\nis back once more! Sunday, starting at 8am PT (Worldclock\n), you have another chance to prove your mettle and walk away with cash and exclusive prizes! Will you end up a proud owner of these fine cosmetics, available for the first time this weekend?\n\u00a0\nJoin us this Sunday and find out!\nFor full details on prizing, please check out our tournament page here\n.\nThe Frostlock AAA card and sleeve are not yet animated. For this upcoming Clash, players will receive a static stand-in which will be upgraded to the animated version in an upcoming patch.\nFor everyone asking about the Uruunaz Blood Starter deck, don't worry! It's almost here. It will also be added in an upcoming patch so you can enjoy it in its full animated glory.\nSee you on the Battlefield~\nGot any questions? Want to chat with other players? Then discuss this article in our Forums\n! You can also follow us on Twitter and Facebook, or enjoy regular streams on our official Twitch channel\n.", "early_access": false}
