{"product_id": "410380", "page": 9, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "text": "The servers will be coming offline today for maintenance and the installation of our major\nupdate! This patch brings a number of fixes and improvements to our game, not to mention a boatload of new content.\nPatch day starts on 6/28 at 10:00 PM PT (Worldclock\n), when we\u2019ll close registrations for new tournaments. Then, on 6/28 at 11:00 PM PT (Worldclock\n), we\u2019ll take the servers offline to give our databases a good scrubbing.\nThe servers and tournaments should come back online on 6/29 at around 12:00 PM PT (Worldclock\n) if everything goes according to plan. Occasionally, while giving our servers a once over, we discover the odd Dreadling or two. Maintenance might last a little longer as a result.\nWe are having an extended downtime this patch as there are some significant improvements to our tournament backend which will require some extra attention this time around. We want you to have the best experience possible when you get your hands on the latest set. Thank you for your patience and understanding!\nTo help with the wait, we will have our release stream\non Thursday, 6/29 at 7am PT to showcase the new set! Join Crota for games, prizes, and to see\nin action. Then, on Friday we will have our release celebration\nto kick off all the fun!\nHere\u2019s the schedule in short-form:\nGot any questions? Want to chat with other players? Then discuss this article in our Forums\n! You can also follow us on Twitter and Facebook, or enjoy regular streams on our official Twitch channel\n.", "early_access": false}
