{"product_id": "658160", "page": 4, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "text": "-Perk levels have no limit now.\n-Rescaled Tome and Rings to bring them back into line(Slight buff on low end amazing nerf on over 20k maxstage end)\n-Chest and Helm were changed but not scaled(They are still hard capped at 30 til i re-work class xp\n-Auto Prestige button that spawns capcha each time you activate it. Stays active for 15min intervals.\n-Change to DPS% on heroes calculation. Might be screwed up depending on the variance of DPS between clicky and heroes currently.(will address in a future build)\n-Fix for gems and wallboss's not spawning after stage 30k", "early_access": false}
