{"product_id": "410380", "page": 12, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "text": "Welcome to a round up of the week! We have game updates, our latest HEX Holiday, and a tournament-filled weekend:\nOur engineers are at it again! This week\nwe have stability fixes and a few UI improvements, like highlighting cards selected in the crypt. Every day HEX grows a little more!\nSpeaking of growth, our spring celebration is on the horizon. Starting April 14th, join us in-game for alternate arts and some new campaign goodies. Egg on your opponents in this verdant jubilee and you can walk away with these fine specimens:\nIf campaign capers are more your style, there are some new PVE cards and equipment to be found as well. But we won't go through the entire gift basket here\u2014crack open all the info in our Feast of Abundance 2017 Announcement\n.\nThe first HexPrimal Immortal Championship tournament\nis only 1 week away! If you plan to join us April 15th, make sure you are jumping into the HEX Primal Immortal queue to get your 20 qualifying tickets.\nRemember, this tournament has some pretty great prizes, including:\n*Contains 1 copy of all cards of a set chosen by HexPrimal.com\nCome for the prizes, stay for some of the craziest card combos HEX has to offer!\nBut if the winds of adventure are calling to you right now, there is no need to delay! Our Platinum Plunder is returning this weekend\n! For you lubbers out there who might not be familiar with the Plunder, this is a free tournament that gives you the opportunity to pillage a cut of 500,000 platinum from our coffers! Join us Saturday, April 8th starting at 9am PT (Worldclock\n) for an adventure on the high seas! Full details on the Platinum Plunder can be found on the main website, here\n.\nAnd to top it all off, the HEX Clash\nis back! This Sunday at 8am PT (Worldclock\n), you have another chance to prove your mettle and walk away with cash and exclusive prizes! Will you end up a proud owner of these fine cosmetics like last week's winners\n?\n\u00a0\nJoin us this Sunday and find out!\nFor full details on prizing, please check out our tournament page here\n.\nNero Jinous, one of our official channel streamers, will be Clashing it up on the hextcg twitch channel once again! Be sure to tune in\nabout 15 minutes before the Clash starts for some pre-game hype. He will be doing HEX-themed games and some limited exercises between rounds, so it should be a party.\nSee you all on the battlefield this Sunday!\nGot any questions? Want to chat with other players? Then discuss this article in our Forums\n! You can also follow us on Twitter and Facebook, or enjoy regular streams on our official Twitch channel\n.", "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "410380", "page": 12, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "text": "Welcome to a round up of the week! Our Feast of Abundance starts today and the HEX Immortal Championship is just around the corner:\nSpeaking of growth, our spring celebration is live! Join us in-game for alternate arts and some new campaign goodies. Egg on your opponents in this verdant jubilee and you can walk away with these fine specimens:\nIf campaign capers are more your style, there are some new PVE cards and equipment to be found as well. But we won't go through the entire gift basket here\u2014crack open all the info in our Feast of Abundance 2017 Announcement\n.\nThe first HexPrimal Immortal Championship tournament\nis this Saturday! If you plan to join us on April 15th, you only have one more day to get your 20 qualifying tickets from the HEX Primal Immortal queue.\nRemember, this tournament has some pretty great prizes, including:\n*Contains 1 copy of all cards of a set chosen by HexPrimal.com\nCome for the prizes, stay for some of the craziest card combos HEX has to offer!\nAnd to top it all off, the HEX Clash\ncontinues going strong! This Sunday at 8am PT (Worldclock\n), you have another chance to prove your mettle and walk away with cash and exclusive prizes! Will you end up a proud owner of these fine cosmetics like last week's winners\n?\n\u00a0\nJoin us Sunday and find out!\nFor full details on prizing, please check out our tournament page here\n.\nNero Jinous, one of our official channel streamers, continues his Clashy tradition this Sunday. Tune in\nto watch Nero's journey in the HEX Clash! Make sure to join him about 15 minutes before the Clash starts for some pre-game hype. He will be doing HEX-themed games and some limited exercises between rounds, so it should be a party.\nSee you all on the battlefield!\nGot any questions? Want to chat with other players? Then discuss this article in our Forums\n! You can also follow us on Twitter and Facebook, or enjoy regul