{"product_id": "410380", "page": 12, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "text": "Welcome to a round up of the week! We have news about our latest battleboards, Kismet's Reserve rotation, tournaments and more!\nThe Canyon battleboard will be rotating out of the Chark Mart soon! If you haven't picked it up already, you have until Thursday, April 27th @ 10:00am PT when the brand-new Castle battleboard will take it's place:\nIf you don't want to be left thirsting for more, don't delay. A new board's on its way!\nThe Kismet's Reserve Silver Talon pack will also be rotating out of Chark Mart in the near future.\nWhile we don't have a date for you just yet, we wanted to give you advanced notice that these exclusive items will be leaving the store. If you want to get your hands on these beautiful birds, be sure to grab them now before they fly away for good!\nWhen we first announced the HEX Clash, we stated that our exclusive Clash cosmetics would rotate\n. After viewing our great turnouts and crunching the numbers a bit more, we have decided to amend this to \"rotate\n\" or every two sets. This change won't have any impact on our current cosmetic lineup as Set 7 is the start of a new HEX chapter\u2014in fact, this means that our AAA Herofalls will be some of the rarest Clash cosmetics around\u2014but we wanted to give you advanced notice of this change. We hope you are enjoying the HEX Clash as much as we are, and we can't wait to show you some of the awesome prizes we have in store as the series continues!\nSpeaking of which:\nThe HEX Clash\nis back again this week! Sunday, starting at 8am PT (Worldclock\n), you have another chance to prove your mettle and walk away with cash and exclusive prizes! Will you end up a proud owner of these fine cosmetics like last week's winners\n?\nJoin us this Sunday and find out!\nFor full details on prizing, please check out our tournament page here\n.\nAs before, Nero Jinous, will be Clashing it up on the hextcg twitch channel while the tournament is in progress! Be sure to tune in\nabout 15 minutes before the Clash starts for some pre-game hype. He will be doing HEX-themed art and some limited exercises between rounds, so it should be a party.\nSee you all on the battlefield this Sunday!\nFinally, our fearless leader, Cory Jones, will be joining the Two Turns Ahead podcast for their 150th episode! If you would like a chance to get your questions asked on the show, make sure you check out this thread on the hextcg reddit.\nGot any questions? Want to chat with other players? Then discuss this article in our Forums\n! You can also follow us on Twitter and Facebook, or enjoy regular streams on our official Twitch channel\n.", "early_access": false}
