{"product_id": "378860", "page": 5, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-01-07", "text": "Honestly can't recommend it. The AI is very inconsistent. They brake too much in corners (causing you to have your exit speed totally ruined), which is extremely frustrating if you're starting at the back, which you will be since they are WAY faster in qualifying than the actual race, on top of varying wildly from circuit to circuit.\nI also have a problem (which I'm not alone in) with the game freezing on me for no discernable reason. The sound and force feedback keep going along with no problem but the image totally freezes and I have no choice but to close the game. This is extremely irritating when I'm winning a race to lose my progress because of this.", "hours": 23.9, "username": "Doomguy", "products": 262, "early_access": false}
