{"product_id": "609150", "page": 14, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-04", "text": "For a full HD Remaster, this game is pretty solid still. The voice acting alone is not as bad as Star Ocean 5, But it's not great either.  However, if you were a fan of the 3rd star ocean, till the end of time. I recommend this over the 5th one. You play the events that lead up to the first Star Ocean game, a Character named Edge, a young boy who wants to become a hero like his Idol, Commander Kenny, (Not same Kenny from the First one)\nCrafting system in the game is indepth, so is the recipes. You can also develop relationships with your crew. Battle is much similar to the 3rd one. I do not have much time on this game for PC, so stability issues I cannot tell you about, however, the game itself I've spent hours on the Xbox playing it. Great game, good story line, Soundtrack in the game is pretty good as well.\nIf you are fan of the star ocean series, I suggest playing this one, It's probably one of the last decent Star Oceans out right now. Score 8/10.", "hours": 1.0, "username": "RazgrizSF", "products": 448, "early_access": false}
