{"product_id": "734580", "page": 20, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-09", "text": "After playing for 2 hours, i got the general idea.\nIt's a fun mix of sandbox and battlefield styled games.\nSo what do you do? you are a soldier, and your goal is to destroy the ennemy base. To do that, you loot stuff to forge materials, ammunitions, build defensive structures, tanks e.t.c.\nGameplay is fun and gunplay is quite interesting.\nFear not, there is no p2w here folks! There are 3 classes that are ''dlc's'' but its not p2w at all + you can get them ingame. and honestly, if you play only one country, then giving 3 euros to get all the available dlc's isnt the end of the world. its a way to support the devs.\nThe game is still in very early ALPHA so a lot of stuff is missing and bugs do exist (tents not working as spawn points for example)\nI would like to suggest a sound overhaul, better textures and the most important for me: Squads with mic. support: Squad leader gets a radio to talk with other squadleaders, and the rest can talk only in local.\nAlso, a medic class would be amazing, same for artylery pieces. the list of suggestion could go on for a loooong time so ill stop here by adding this: This game has a huge potential. This could become the best ww2 game we have right now, don't let it die.", "hours": 11.8, "username": "thelyraki", "products": 60, "early_access": true}
