{"product_id": "410380", "page": 25, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "text": "Greetings everyone!\nOn 03/11/2016 the servers will be undergoing maintenance, during which time we'll be installing a new update for you.\nWe will be bringing down the server for routine back-end maintenance. Additionally, we are taking this opportunity to streamline the initial Steam account creation process. New accounts through Steam will no longer have to go through the game account creation process.\nThings start Wednesday the 2nd at 10pm PST (6am CET), when we'll close registrations for new tournaments. Then, on Thursday the 3rd at 1am PT (10am CET), we'll take the servers offline. If everything runs according to plan, the servers will reopen their gates to you again at 6:30am PST (2:30pm CET).\nNote: Occasionally, while giving our servers a once over, we discover a spider egg in the deck or catch a shroomkin chewing on one of the cables. When that happens, it sometimes takes a little longer before everything is back online.\nThanks for your patience and understanding!\n10pm PST (06:00 CET)  \u2013 Tournament servers lock\n2am PST (10:00 CET)  \u2013 Servers offline\n6:30am PST (14:30 CET)  \u2013 Expected end to maintenance", "early_access": false}
