{"product_id": "410380", "page": 28, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "text": "Something wicked (awesome) this way comes! It's this year's Haunted Harvest, complete with new alternate arts, sleeves, and exclusive campaign cards and equipment for you to collect. The Haunted Harvest will run from October 18th to November 1st, so break out your scythe and get ready to reap! Check out our full post\nfor more details.\nOur second ladder season is nearing a close, so it's climb time for anyone who wants to join us for our next Cosmic Crown Showdown! The cutoff is midnight Pacific, Oct 31st which is just two short weeks away. Don't delay!\nOur Cosmic Crown Showdown is also going through some small changes to our terms and conditions. We are taking some steps to ensure that the finals of the Showdown are as exciting as possible. All the info you need can be found in this post here\n.\nLast weekend was the Radiant Rumble. Congratulations to Justiis for a $2,000 finish! The Radiant Rumble was our largest community tournament to date, and you guys knocked it out of the park. There were a ton of exciting deck variants\nwhich took to the field and the community coverage was top notch! If you haven't already, make sure you watch the event on the FiveShards twitch page\n.\nWe are still looking for an exceptional UI artist to join the HEX team. If you are interested in helping us design the best user experience possible for our game, please check out our listing here\n. At HEX we believe in taking talent from the qualified people who support us every day. If you have a passion for our game and think you have what it takes, please make sure to submit an application. We look forward to hearing from you!", "early_access": false}
