{"product_id": "410380", "page": 28, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "text": "We have just retired the current slate of Starter Decks from the HEX store. In their place we are offering a selection of pre-built, highly-competitive deck options to provide a jumping off point for the HEX Constructed scene.\nIf you\u2019ve ever wanted to climb the ladder but didn\u2019t know where to start, these decks will give you a painless way to start playing today. Our Signature Decks are between 1200 and 1500 platinum, offer unique and interesting entry-level strategies, and are designed by some of the most experienced deck-builders our community has to offer! Let\u2019s take a look:\nSet your opponents ablaze with this powerful deck designed by Jeff Hoogland. Become a master of the flame by maximizing every point of damage with your sequencing of aggressive troops and actions. The best defense is a good offense!\n--\nDesigned by TCG analyst Varranis, Pathfinder Control allows you to use your wits to out maneuver your opponents. Built around comboing a Replicator\u2019s Gambit on a prophesied Starlight Pathfinder, this deck provides a cerebral path to victory. Timing your Countermagic, removal, and damage mitigation is critical to surviving until you can unleash your one-two punch.\n--\nArdent Assault is an aggressive deck designed by Chris VanMeter that focuses on efficient troops and the synergies provided by the Ardent faction. Key troops like Warparty Guide and Ardent Officer greatly reward you for having a healthy stockpile of Ardent Troops, both in play and in your deck. Defend your lands and people from the Horrors of War! Beat back the Underworld and be ready to launch a full-on Ardent Assault!\n--\nIt\u2019s never been easier to dive into Constructed HEX. See you on the battlefield!", "early_access": false}
