{"product_id": "347400", "page": 6, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "text": "We\u2019re pleased to announce that our long anticipated MMORPG Kit is now live on Steam! Available for\n, this DLC expansion adds a new project type to 001 Game Creator allowing anyone to create full blown MMORPGs! Please see our\nfor a full list of features.\nWe\u2019ve also updated 001 Game Creator to v1.018.003 to address a few issues found with our last update and to ensure complete compatibility with the MMORPG Kit. Please see our\nfor all the details.\nLastly, to celebrate the launch of our first DLC kit, I\u2019m pleased to announce that 001 Game Creator will be\n.\nWe\u2019d like to thank all of those involved for their hard work and to our passionate community who have supported us over the years. We hope you\u2019ll look forward to our upcoming FPS and Point & Click Adventure DLC Kits that we\u2019ll be rolling out in the coming months! :)", "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "410380", "page": 29, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "text": "Put your Primal Dawn packs aside and embrace the new adventure that is Herofall, the latest\nset!\nFrom Friday, September 9th at 19:00 CET (10 AM PST) to Monday, September 12th at 18:59 CET (9:59 AM PST), we\u2019re making all our\nformats a party with exclusive prizes.\nAll Limited tournaments will feature two new Alternate Art cards.\nYou will get an Alternate Art\nfor participation. To earn the Alternate Art\n, you have to win (in Draft) or achieve 5 wins (in Evolving Sealed and Sealed).\nHere\u2019s an overview of how to get them:\nHerofall Sealed Gauntlet\n\u2022 Participation = Waylay AA\n\u2022 5 wins = Swampwater Recluse AA\nHerofall Evolving Sealed Gauntlet\n\u2022 Participation = Waylay AA\n\u2022 5 Wins = Swampwater Recluse AA\nHerofall Competitive Draft\n\u2022 Participation = Waylay AA\n\u2022 1st Place = Swampwater Recluse AA\nGood luck and enjoy the games!", "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "410380", "page": 29, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "text": "The fifth card set for\nis now available in-game, bringing with it over 275 new cards, Champions, Gems and Equipment.\nWe are super happy to have our fifth card set,\n, open its doors for you today!\nIf you somehow managed to avoid all the juicy bits of information for this expansion, read on to get an idea of what\u2019s happening:\n\u2022\tHerofall fully available\n\u2022\t275 new cards\n\u2022\t4 new keywords\n\u2022\t20 new Champions\n\u2022\t20 completely new gems\nThis release marks the next highlight in a year filled with them \u2013 and what a year it\u2019s been so far: we released the first ever PvE update, hosted a $100,000 tournament, brought the game to Steam, published Set 4 and created our ladder system.\nCome join us in this latest expansion for\n!", "early_access": false}
