{"product_id": "410380", "page": 30, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "text": "Welcome to HEX's second ladder season!\nWe hope you enjoyed Season 1 of the Ladder. Let's See what you can expect from Season 2.\nFirst, you will keep the highest sleeve you earned during Season 1, but all other cosmetic items (including plinths, sleeves, and rank) will be reset for Season 2. Highly ranked players will receive a small boost in their initial ladder ranking so that all players can enjoy a smooth climbing experience.\nSecond, players will continue to be able to earn gold, packs, and Alternate Arts by climbing the Limited and Constructed ladders. This season, we have the following Alternate Arts up for grabs:\nThose who reach Cosmic will also receive a season exclusive animated sleeve! You voted on it, so we are extremely excited to reveal our animated Alternate Art Shardcall sleeves.\n\nhttps://www.hextcg.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/CosmicSeason02.mp4\nThird, we will be back granting an extra <em>Herofall</em> pack to anyone who earns a\npack in the Season 2 Ladder before the release of our 5th set.\nFinally, we want to remind everyone that the Ladder system is an evolving thing. Please keep leaving your feedback for us on the forums. It is invaluable as we work to grow the Ladder into its best possible form.", "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "410380", "page": 30, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "text": "We can\u2019t wait for you to get your hands on the new cards and to play with the many new strategies and tactics opened up by the many additions to our game. The appetite you showed over these last few weeks for spoilers, new lore and gameplay mechanics will finally be sated.\nWe are certain that you will enjoy this expansion immensely!\nIn these coming days before the launch of our new card set, we will have the final bits of information for you, such as our launch celebration and patch notes.\nWe would also like to make you aware that the first week of Ladder Season 2 is going to be played before the launch of Herofall. To accommodate this rather short transition time, we will grant you a booster pack of Herofall in addition to the Primal Dawn booster packs you would receive at the appropriate reward tiers. These booster packs will be granted retroactively after the release of Herofall.\nWith the launch of Herofall, we will be replacing the Orc Mage Sleeve as the reward for completing three Evolving Sealed Gauntlets.\nIf you haven\u2019t already grabbed your copy today, make sure you do so by September 7th!\nWhen Herofall releases, we will introduce a brand-new sleeve earned by playing in three Evolving Sealed Gauntlets. Check it out:\nYou will still be able to get the Orc Mage Sleeve by purchasing the Primal Dawn Steam DLC, as the sleeve will remain unchanged there.\nGame on!", "early_access": false}
