{"product_id": "410380", "page": 35, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "text": "Join us between the 2nd of May at 10 AM PDT (19:00 CET) until the 16th of May at 9:59 AM PDT (18:59 CET) to earn these prosperous and bountiful rewards of spring!\nThe first time a player logs in during this holiday, they will receive a Feast of Abundance sleeve. This will be the art from the Cheery Songbird.\nAll tournaments will have a participation prize of an AA Cheery Songbird\ncard. Basically, enter a tournament, get the card.\nPlayers can earn PvE items by playing in the Campaign dungeons. There is one card and two equipment items to earn. By defeating any dungeon you will earn one of the three items at random. Each of them has a percent chance to drop: 15% on the Rare Equipment, 25% on the Uncommon Equipment, and 60% on the Card.\nSymeon\u2019s Bounty\nFruit of Symeon\nRare \u2013 Fruit Pluckers\nUncommon \u2013 Grafted Stave", "early_access": false}
