{"product_id": "658160", "page": 7, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "text": "-Season is Primed and ready to go!\n-Added Perk system, More you level your classes the better passive perks you will gain. These are self only...\n-Fixed a bunch of damage calculations relating to Global Damage and Tome\n-Revisited tome and went with a cap of level 25.\n-Increased the Multiplier on Unique gear and made it slightly harder to obtain it now sits between legendary and exotic.", "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "658160", "page": 7, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "text": "-Complete re-write on the playerlist functionality(way better performance)\n-Added Shaded button for active talent preset\n-Fixed cursor odd 1 pixel off type thing that was going on for awhile.\n-Fixed a firearrow tick damage bug\n-Added a total level limit display to playerlist\n-Increased spacing on playerlist so things looked less bad\n-Removed a bunch of string calls from existing code that were eating performance\n-Removed delay from playerlist stats showing.\n-Increased speed of Damage gems to charm\n-Tavern button only lights up if you have the bossouls for a quest.", "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "658160", "page": 7, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "text": "-Changed to a more hybrid spawn system that gives some room for spawns and everything else. Should result in a smoother experience.\n-Changed Sync timings so 20 things dont sync at the same time.\n-Fixed a few playerlist bugs with player data not cleared when leaving and other abnormalitys.\n-Fixed a bunch of surface issues(should free up some GPU)\n-Fixed a Tome Bug\n-Unloaded ALL sounds when volume slider at the lowest setting", "early_access": false}
