{"product_id": "410380", "page": 36, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "text": "More Streaming news!\nCome join Infam0usne0, Alucard and the rest of our star studded cast of HEXTCG Streamers as we launch Primal Dawn with an extra special 48h long stream!\nThese streams are valuable to everyone!  Tune in at our official HEXTCG channel\nand learn the various tricks of the game from our awesome streamers!\nWe'll see you there!", "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "410380", "page": 36, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "text": "Greetings everyone!\nPrimal Dawn has been released! Our players are now cracking open packs, playing tournaments and exploring all the new cards that are a part of this set.\nA couple of quick updates for you:\nGameforge and Hex Entertainment have listened to your feedback and granted additional platinum to players who purchased via Steam on the old prices. The platinum was sent out during the Primal Dawn update downtime. We feel that it is the right thing to do and apologise for any inconvenience this may have caused.\nSecondly, to celebrate the release of Primal Dawn, we have also given each existing account a free Evolution Sealed Gauntlet ticket. This is a new tournament format for the budget-minded player and we want to make sure that players are able to enjoy competitive PvP tournaments regardless of their spending patterns.\nAn article explaining this new format can be found here\n\nFinally, we have just deplayed a fix for the in-game mail system, so you should no longer be plagued by lag when opening messages.\nTill nex time,\nHappy Hexing and may Kismet smile upon you", "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "410380", "page": 36, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "text": "Greetings everyone,\nThe fourth card set for HEX: Shards of Fate is now available in-game, bringing over 300 new cards, Champions and Equipment into the world of Entrath.\nHaving launched on Steam just last week, the next huge milestone is here: during today\u2019s maintenance, we have published the long-awaited \u201cPrimal Dawn\u201d expansion. In case you\u2019ve miraculously not heard anything at all about the fourth card set, here\u2019s the low down:\nIn celebration of the new, exciting tournament format, we are giving every player who logged in within in the last 30 days a free entry ticket to the new queue!\nSo what are you waiting for? Log in and get your HEX on!\nPlease also join us for the release celebration of the newly published content from April 29 to May 2.\nStay tuned for more info!\nGame on", "early_access": false}
