{"product_id": "410380", "page": 39, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "text": "It is finally happening: HEX will be available on Steam starting 19/04/2016. You\u2019ll then be able to add our game to your games library, download it and play. The game will naturally be remaining free to play!\nIf you already have an account, you can simply link it and then log in via Steam \u2013 doing so is quick and easy!\nYou can also of course purchase our premium currency via Steam. In the future, we will also be offering bundles that comprise of booster packs and some pretty neat surprises.\nAs is usual with Steam, HEX will also be automatically updated via the service, enabling you to always be up-to-date without having to worry about anything.\nEnjoy HEX \u2013 via Steam!\nThe HEX Team", "early_access": false}
